.TH RODIN\-HEADLESS 1 "2026-06-24" "rodin-headless @VERSION@" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
rodin\-headless \- headless Event\-B build, model\-check, and proof runner
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B rodin\-headless
.RI [ command ]
.RI [ \-\-strict ]
.RI [ model.zip ...]
.br
.B rodin\-headless
.RB [ \-\-version | \-V ]
.br
.B rodin\-headless
.B help
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B rodin\-headless
feeds
.I .zip
archives containing Event\-B models through Rodin's headless static checker
and, optionally, ProB validation or the SMT/Atelier\ B auto\-provers, writing
the generated artifacts
.RB ( .bcm ", " .bcc ", " .bpo ", " .bps ", " .bpr )
back into each archive in place.
.PP
It picks a runtime automatically: a native Rodin install when one is present
(see
.BR rodin\-headless\-install (1)),
otherwise the prebuilt Docker image
.RB ( docker " or " podman ).
The selection is controlled by
.BR RODIN_RUNTIME .
.PP
If no command is given,
.B build
is assumed. If no archives are listed, every
.I .zip
in the current directory is processed.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B build " [zips...]"
Build the models with Rodin (the default).
.TP
.B check " [zips...]"
Build, then model\-check with ProB (bounded, 1000 states).
.TP
.B prove " [zips...]"
Build, then run ProB constraint\-based invariant checking.
.TP
.B validate " [zips...]"
Build, then full ProB validation (invariants, deadlock, assertions).
.TP
.B autoprove " [zips...]"
Build, then discharge proof obligations with SMT and Atelier\ B tactics.
.TP
.B probcli " [args...]"
Run
.B probcli
directly with arbitrary arguments.
.TP
.B help
Print usage and exit. Requires no runtime, install, or image.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-strict
Exit non\-zero when any component fails Rodin's static check or was never
checked (including multi\-project archives). May appear anywhere after the
command word.
.TP
.BR \-\-version ", " \-V
Print the program version and exit.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B RODIN_RUNTIME
Runtime selection:
.BR auto " (default), " native ", " docker ", or " podman .
.TP
.B RODIN_DIR
Path to a Rodin install to use directly (must contain
.IR rodin.ini ).
.TP
.B RODIN_PREFIX
Native install prefix searched in auto mode
.RI ( default " ~/.local/share/rodin-headless" ).
.TP
.B RODIN_IMAGE
Container image reference
.RI ( default " ghcr.io/eventb-rossi/rodin-headless:latest" ).
.TP
.B RODIN_BUILD_LOCAL
When set, build the image from the local Dockerfile instead of pulling.
.TP
.B RODIN_BUILD_TIMEOUT
Build timeout
.RI ( default " 60m" ;
.B off
disables it);
.B RODIN_BUILD_TIMEOUT_KILL_AFTER
sets the grace period after the timeout
.RI ( default " 30s" ).
.TP
.B RODIN_PLATFORM
Override platform detection
.RB ( linux\-x86_64 ", " macos\-x86_64 ", " macos\-aarch64 ).
.TP
.B RODIN_HEADLESS_LIBEXEC
Directory holding the engine library and helper scripts. Set by the
installed wrapper; override only for unusual layouts.
.TP
.B RODIN_HEADLESS_DATADIR
Directory holding the Docker build context used for a local image build.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success.
.TP
.B 1
A runtime or usage error, or (with
.BR \-\-strict )
a component that failed or was not statically checked.
.TP
.B 124
The build timed out.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I <prefix>/.rodin-headless-versions
Manifest of the resolved Rodin and ProB versions for a native install.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR rodin\-headless\-install (1),
.BR probcli (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Denis Efremov.
